### GraphQL Health Check Query
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ users { id name email is_active } }"
}

###

### Get Users
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { users { id name email is_active created_at updated_at } }"
}

###

### Get User By ID
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { user(id: 1) { id name email is_active } }"
}

###

### Create User
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { createUser(name:\"GraphQL User\", email:\"graphql@test.com\") { id name email } }"
}
###

### Update User
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query":"mutation{updateUser(id:1,name:\"Updated User\",email:\"updated@test.com\"){id name email}}"
}
###

### Delete User
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation { deleteUser(id:1) }"
}